nodes.text: Nahrunba was a male Dug who served under Sebolto's employ during the waning years of the Galactic Republic. In 32 BBY, he was wanted for being the youngest one of the three Dug brothers, the others being Jahrunba and Sahrunba, who smuggled numerous death sticks to the Gran Youth Council of Pixelito. His bounty worth 3,000 credits alive and 1,500 credits dead was claimed by Jango Fett.
